# Xcode / Swift — https://github.com/github/gitignore/blob/main/Swift.gitignore

## macOS
.DS_Store

## User settings & build state
xcuserdata/
*.xcuserstate
*.xcscmblueprint
*.xccheckout

## Build products
build/
DerivedData/
*.moved-aside
